latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Dance can actually help. Those who practice transcendental meditation may experience a decrease in stress and anxiety within minutes. As with other forms of meditation, long-term practice can lead to even more positive changes, including resilience to stress, lower overall anxiety, and even greater life satisfaction.

What is Transcendental Meditaiton ?

The deepest state of Transcendental Meditaiton is when the brain is no longer  processing data from the outside world. The state of Being is one of pure consciousness, completely out of the ﬁeld of relativity; there is no world of the senses or of objects, no trace of sensory activity, no trace of mental activity. There is no trinity of thinker, thinking process and thought, process of doing and action; experiencer, process of experiencing and object of experience. The state of transcendentalUnity of life, or pure consciousness, is completely free from all trace of duality.”

People will laugh and make fun. But we never give up on our authentic self. We don't just survive... We LIVE!

I miss you all and I'll see you soon again.

latestPosts.caption:
The Glow I Guard 🌻

Total Defence, my morning shield,
Soft as silk, yet strong in yield.
The sun may rise without a care,
But I meet its touch, fully aware.

No white cast, no heavy veil,
Just calm where breakouts used to trail.
It soothes, it blends, it lets me be—
A canvas breathing, wild and free.

From bare to bold, I shift with grace,
Gold on skin, light on face.
In every climate, in every scene,
Total Defence keeps my temple clean.

#SunSafeAndStunning #DragSkincare #GlowingWithSPF

🌈 In the journey toward embracing one’s true identity, ethical support systems—both from inclusive NGOs and affirming mental health professionals—can make all the difference.

Sometimes, a mental health professional becomes the mirror we never knew we needed—a gentle, nonjudgmental presence who helps us explore the parts of ourselves we were too afraid to touch. In their compassion, we find the courage to come home to our truth.

In this heartfelt dialogue, we explore the incredible work of organizations like @naazfoundationofficial, as shared by the inspiring @hiten.noonwal , and discuss how mental health professionals can walk alongside LGBTQ+ individuals with sensitivity, respect, and affirmation.

Together, let’s keep building safer spaces, where healing and authenticity go hand in hand. 💜

latestPosts.caption:
Hand-Painted Bloom
Wearable inspiration from nature - Each petal whispered a story. I painted them with care, like fragments of a dream.
Orchids - delicate, sensual, wild… 
Became my canvas, my muse, my mask.

What began as petals bloomed into identity. A face that hides nothing, only reveals beauty in layers. This isn’t just a mask. It’s a metamorphosis.
Nature worn. Art breathed.

#OrchidMask #WearableArt #NatureCouture #BotanicalFantasy #HandmadeMagic #DragArtistry #QueerArtIndia #SustainableDesign #FloralFantasy #ArtInBloom
